a999c231-d3a6-45f6-9650-711d8e544b50.title: Quest Guide
a999c231-d3a6-45f6-9650-711d8e544b50.text:
Ah! Welcome, adventurer. I'm here to tell you all about
quests. Let's start by opening the quest journal.

7e0007c7-a565-4744-a937-3f062bb6f94d.title: Quest Guide
7e0007c7-a565-4744-a937-3f062bb6f94d.text:
Now you have the journal open I'll tell you a bit about
it. At the moment all the quests are shown in red, which
means you have not started them yet.

81bf786c-7d73-4c19-8dc5-494860f485f3.title: Quest Guide
81bf786c-7d73-4c19-8dc5-494860f485f3.text:
When you start a quest it will change colour to yellow,
and to green when you've finished. This is so you can
easily see what's complete, what's started, and what's left
to begin.

5fed5ac2-8c75-4479-a7af-6815f56edcf0.title: Quest Guide
5fed5ac2-8c75-4479-a7af-6815f56edcf0.text:
The start of quests are easy to find. Look out for the
star icons on the minimap, just like the one you should
see marking my house.

f2abc6c3-e766-4c59-9645-cbb14b83f5d3.title: Quest Guide
f2abc6c3-e766-4c59-9645-cbb14b83f5d3.text:
The quests themselves can vary greatly from collecting
beads to hunting down dragons. Generally quests are
started by talking to a non-player character like me,
and will involve a series of tasks.

fef6aa90-7524-41c8-a58a-fcd3a9830bba.title: Quest Guide
fef6aa90-7524-41c8-a58a-fcd3a9830bba.text:
There's not a lot more I can tell you about questing.
You have to experience the thrill of it yourself to fully
understand. You may find some adventure in the caves
under my house.

b37e2e41-f679-4ea3-b053-eeeb2da0ea94.title: Would you like to hear about quests again?

options.text: Nope, I'm ready to move on!

3b30c928-c55c-43cb-bf97-2bb42f6ad8ef.title: Quest Guide
3b30c928-c55c-43cb-bf97-2bb42f6ad8ef.text:
If you open your quest menu you will see that at the
moment all the quests are shown in red, a quest shown
in red is unstarted.
